      <div class="uu-main-column">
       <div class="uu-main-content">
        <h2>
         News and Announcements
        </h2>
        <p>
         In April 2017 the TVC Intellectual Property database was moved to a hosted vendor
                           solution and, as a result, the integration between Business Relationship Reporting
                           (BRR) and TVC is no longer functional. Subsequently, any Intellectual Property disclosed
                           to TVC since the database move will need to be manually entered into BRR as part of
                           the attestation process. We apologize for this inconvenience and appreciate your patience
                           while we attempt to restore the integration with the new TVC solution as soon as possible.
                           If you have questions or concerns regarding the Individual Conflict of Interest Policy,
                           please contact the COI Office by email at coi@hsc.utah.edu or by phone at 587-3232.
        </p>
        <h2>
         About the COI Office
        </h2>
        <p>
         The
         <a href="/contact.php">
          Conflict of Interest Office
         </a>
         supports the University community in identifying and managing financial conflicts
                           of interest in three areas:
        </p>
        <ul>
         <li>
          Research and Scholarly Activities
         </li>
         <li>
          Procurement
         </li>
         <li>
          Intellectual Property
         </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
         We work with faculty, staff, postdoctoral fellows, students and others who are required
                           to disclose external financial interests to the University for evaluation.  We also
                           work with the
         <a href="/roster.php">
          Individual Conflict of Interest Committee
         </a>
         to review and manage financial interests that create conflicts of interest.
        </p>
